## Acceptance check

- **B1** — page is single long-scroll with sections in order: Typography → Color → Spacing → Motion → Primitives. Each has a numbered header and serif framing paragraph citing v2_principles by number (6, 7, 4, 8/10, 4).
- **B2** — `TypeSpecimen` renders each `.t-*` utility (`t-headline`, `t-h1`, `t-h2`, `t-h3`, `t-prose`, `t-mono-body`, `t-meta`, `t-code`) with the pangram, class label, size and line-height.
- **B3** — `ColorSwatch` reads tokens at runtime via `getComputedStyle`, displays hex, and computes WCAG contrast vs. `--bg` and `--bg-mute`. A `MutationObserver` re-reads on `data-theme` changes; `ThemeToggle` flips between dark/light.
- **B4** — `SpacingRuler` renders each `--s-1`…`--s-10` as a labelled horizontal bar.
- **B5** — `MotionDemo` renders five demos (one per duration token) with play buttons; `prefers-reduced-motion` collapses the transition duration to 0 so it completes instantly.
- **B6** — `PrimitiveGallery` renders Button (variant × tone × size, plus disabled and loading), Link (underline/subtle/external), Surface (base/mute/raise), Card (static/linked), Badge (neutral/accent/warn/ok).
- **B7** — page-level `metadata.robots = { index: false, follow: false }` ⇒ confirmed `noindex, nofollow` in served HTML. Page is not added to the public navigation.

